<Layout title="Privacy Policy | 4x10.dev">
    <main class="legal-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="legal-content reveal">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                
                <p>We take the protection of your personal data seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how information may be collected and used when you visit this website.</p>

                <p>We may collect basic information you provide (for example, when you contact us), along with limited technical data (such as browser or device details) to operate the website and improve your experience.</p>

                <p>We do not sell your data. Information may be shared only when necessary to run the website or comply with legal obligations.</p>

                <p>This website may use cookies or similar technologies. You can manage them through your browser settings.</p>

                <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information and retain it only as long as necessary.</p>

                <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete your data.</p>

                <p>By using this website, you agree to this policy. For any questions, please contact us.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
